ic Income FundFranklin Global Trust - Franklin Large Cap Equity FundFranklin Strategic Series - Franklin Small-Mid Cap Growth FundFranklin Strategic Series - Franklin Growth Opportunities FundFranklin Custodian Funds - Franklin DynaTech FundFranklin Global Communications FundFranklin Strategic Series -Technology FundFranklin Strategic Series - Franklin Blue Chip FundTempleton Funds - Templeton Foreign FundTempleton Funds - Templeton World FundTempleton Developing Markets TrustTempleton Institutional Funds - Emerging Markets SeriesTempleton Institutional Funds - International Equity SeriesFranklin Investors Securities Trust - Franklin Equity Income FundFranklin Investors Securities Trust - Franklin Convertible Securities FundTempleton Global Investment Trust - Templeton Foreign Smaller Companies FundSantander Consumer USA Holdings Inc.Franklin Capital Growth FundThe Kraft Heinz Foods Company


