Insider Activity


Individual




Edith E. Holiday



Ms. Edith E. Holiday is Independent Trustee at Franklin Ltd. Duration Income Trust, Independent Director at White Mountains Insurance Group Ltd., Independent Trustee at Franklin Universal Trust, Independent Director at Canadian National Railway Co., Lead Independent Trustee at Templeton Emerging Markets Income Fund, Lead Independent Trustee at Templeton Emerging Markets Fund, Lead Independent Director at Templeton Russia & East European Fund, Inc., Lead Independent Director at Templeton Dragon Fund, Inc., Lead Independent Trustee at Templeton Global Income Fund, Independent Director at Hess Corp., a Member at State Bar of Georgia, a Member at State Bar of Florida, and a Member at The District of Columbia Bar. She is on the Board of Directors at Franklin Ltd. Duration Income Trust, White Mountains Insurance Group Ltd., Franklin Universal Trust, Canadian National Railway Co., Templeton Emerging Markets Income Fund, Templeton Emerging Markets Fund, Templeton Russia & East European Fund, Inc., Templeton Dragon Fund, Inc., Templeton Global Income Fund, Hess Corp., and Investment Company Institute.
Ms. Holiday was previously employed as President, Secretary & Treasurer by Comcast TW Holdings, Inc., a Trustee by Franklin Multi Income Trust, a Trustee by TWE Holdings I Trust, a Trustee by TWE Holdings II Trust, Independent Director by RTI International Metals, Inc., Independent Director by H.J. Heinz Co., and General Counsel by US Department of The Treasury. She also served on the board at Golden Gate National Senior Care LLC.
She received her undergraduate degree from the University of Florida and a graduate degree from the University of Florida.



